\lang1033\ltrch\f2\fs36\b\i0\ul0\cf2\cb10\ is with child\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\  This is actually the future, as we find concerning Manoah’s wife, that the angel said to 
\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ her (Judges 13:3): “And you shall conceive and bear a son,” and it is written, “Behold, you are with 
